# Data processing Package

- Requirements
    - pandas
    - pyreadstat
    - numpy
    - zipfile
    - fastapi[UploadFile]


- __init__(files, file_name, is_qme):
```
files: list[UploadFile] default = None
file_name: str default = ''
is_qme: bool default = True
```
